<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8177875>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. Stockumites kleinerae (Korn, 1984) from Gattendorf. A. Cross section of specimen MB.C.31261 (Korn 1989 Coll.) from bed 21a. B. Cross section of specimen SMF Mbg.7561 (Schindewolf 1916 Coll.) from bed 21. C. Cross section of specimen SMF Mbg.7562 (Schindewolf 1916 Coll.) from bed 21. D. Cross section of specimen MB.C.31262.1 (Korn 1989 Coll.) from bed 21c–d. E–G. Ontogenetic development of the conch width index (ww/dm), umbilical width index (uw/dm), whorl width index (ww/wh) and whorl expansion rate (WER) of selected specimens. Scale bar units =1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8177875/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

